(349, 1, '2010-10-19 22:22:44', '2010-10-19 20:22:44', '<h2><strong>DATES</strong></h2>\r\nConference: <strong>5th to 7th November 2010</strong>\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>The  registration has been closed. Please, pay the registration fee until  <span style="text-decoration: underline;">22.10.2010</span>. If you do not pay it until this day, your registation will  be declined. </strong></span>\r\n<h2><strong>FEES</strong></h2>\r\nDelegates from Slovakia without accommodation: <strong>35€</strong>\r\nDelegates from Slovakia with accommodation: <strong>65€</strong>\r\nDelegates from abroad: <strong>105€</strong>\r\n\r\nRegistration fee includes three nights accommodation with breakfast and lunch during the conference, plus dinner at the banquet. Transportation to Bratislava is<strong> not included</strong> in the registration fee.\r\nAll delegations from one school must have a teacher - faculty advisor accompanying them. The tfaculty advisor will need to be registered as well, but <strong>won’t</strong> be paying any fee.', 'Dates and fees', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '32-revision-17', '', '', '2010-10-19 22:22:44', '2010-10-19 20:22:44', '', 32, 'http://bratmun.sk/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
