(23, '<h2 style="text-align: center; ">\r\n	Information for Press</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n	Press representatives, freelance journalists, TV reporters and PR&#39;s are sincerely welcomed on BratMUN 2011. In order to receive the accreditation for the conference, please send a copy of your Press Card (in case of press representatives), a copy/link of the most recent article related to BratMUN 2011 (in case of freelance journalists), a confirmation from TV channel about assignment to do a coverage on BratMUN 2011 (in case of TV reporters), and portofolio of the companies working for (only in case of PR&#39;s) - please send the material with an accompanying word to <a href="mailto:bratmun@bratmun.sk">bratmun@bratmun.sk</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n	Please notice that based on the fact the conference takes place in the venue of National Council,&nbsp;formal Western Business Attire is required for everyone.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; ">\r\n	In case you&#39;ll be accredited, please bring your ID card with you and your Press Card, in case you have one.</p>\r\n', 'press_main');
