(24, '<p>\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" face="georgia, serif" size="4"><b>Invitation</b></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 12.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Arial; color: #232323">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif;"><span style="color:#ffffff;">We live in a very fluctuant and unstable world.&nbsp; All the same, most of us are usually concerned only by our own problems .&nbsp; But sometimes it is useful to think of the problems people have at the other ends of the world, in order to gain a greater perspective. Our representatives at the UN aren&rsquo;t the only ones who should be acquainted with the international issues, after all, even they can make wrong decisions. Therefore it is you, the new generation, who should become more internationally focused and get rid of the black and white answers. MUNs are offering you all of these aspects and are willing to show you the grey areas too.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 15.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px Georgia; color: #ffffff">\r\n	<span style="font-family:georgia,serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#ffffff;">In the last few months we were witnesses of a number of significant happenings at the international level. None of the western powers ha</span>s made any effective steps to throw down &ldquo;the last European Dictator&rdquo; and to implement real democratic elections in Belorussia. Current happenings in African Muslim states remind&nbsp; us of a massively spreading forest fire, which is &ldquo;burning down&rdquo; the aut</span>ocratic leaders. The intervention in Libya seems to be a high-stakes gam</span>ble with the political attitude and mainly the lives of all involved civilians, its consequences are unknown. The list just seems to be endless.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 15.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px Georgia; color: #ffffff">\r\n	It is you who will have to face such modern-day problems at BratMUN. Furthermore I can promise that BratMUN 2011 will certainly be a conference to remeber, mainly due to the admiring efforts of our organizing team. Therefore with a great pleasure I would like to invite you to BratMUN 2011, whose registration is opening on the 5th of September - don&#39;t hesitate and join us.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 15.0px 0.0px; font: 15.0px Georgia; color: #ffffff">\r\n	Dominik Hatiar</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 15.0px 0.0px; font: 15.0px Georgia; color: #ffffff">\r\n	Main Manager</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 'none_invitation');
